<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>瑠璃フクロウ｜アプリ＆攻略情報</title>
<meta name="description" content="瑠璃フクロウのアプリ・イベント攻略ブログ。同人イベントをもっと便利に。">
<link rel="icon" href="/icon.png" type="image/png">

<style>
  :root{
    --navy:#0c1a38;
    --navy2:#142c54;
    --orange:#f5821f;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  body{
    font-family:"Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN","Yu Gothic",YuGothic,"Meiryo",sans-serif;
    background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--navy) 0%,var(--navy2) 100%);
    color:#fff; min-height:100vh; line-height:1.7;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  .wrap{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:56px 24px 64px}

  .head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:44px}
  .brand{font-size:15px;color:#aebfe0;letter-spacing:.08em}
  .title{font-size:34px;font-weight:800;margin-top:8px}
  .title .o{color:var(--orange)}
  .lead{font-size:15px;color:#9fb0d4;margin-top:12px}

  .section-label{
    font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#7f8eb0;letter-spacing:.1em;
    margin-bottom:14px;padding-left:2px;
  }

  .apps{display:grid;gap:18px;margin-bottom:40px}
  .card{
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;text-decoration:none;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    border-radius:20px;padding:20px 22px;color:#fff;
    transition:transform .12s ease,background .12s ease;
  }
  .card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);background:rgba(255,255,255,.10)}
  .card .icon{
    width:74px;height:74px;border-radius:17px;flex:0 0 auto;background:#fff;
    box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.3);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    object-fit:cover;
  }
  .card .body{flex:1 1 auto;min-width:0}
  .card .name{font-size:21px;font-weight:800}
  .card .desc{font-size:13.5px;color:#aebfe0;margin-top:3px}
  .card .meta{font-size:12px;color:#7f8eb0;margin-top:6px}
  .card .arrow{flex:0 0 auto;color:var(--orange);font-size:22px;font-weight:800}

  .blog-badge{
    width:74px;height:74px;border-radius:17px;flex:0 0 auto;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange), #e06a00);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;letter-spacing:.06em;
    box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(245,130,31,.3);
  }

  footer{
    text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#7f8eb0;
    border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding-top:24px;
  }
  footer a{color:#9fb0d4}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <div class="head">
    <div class="brand">瑠璃フクロウ</div>
    <div class="title">同人イベントを、<span class="o">もっと便利に。</span></div>
    <div class="lead">アプリ・攻略情報をまとめてお届け</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-label">APPS</div>
  <div class="apps">

    <a class="card" href="/torehan/">
      <img class="icon" src="/icon.png" alt="とれはんっ！" onerror="this.style.visibility='hidden'">
      <div class="body">
        <div class="name">とれはんっ！</div>
        <div class="desc">同人イベント攻略アプリ｜お品書きAI読み取り・サークル分担・会場マップ・軍資金/おつり計算</div>
        <div class="meta">App Store 公開中・基本無料</div>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow">&rsaquo;</div>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/urehan/">
      <img class="icon" src="/urehan/icon.png" alt="レジさぽっ！" onerror="this.style.visibility='hidden'">
      <div class="body">
        <div class="name">レジさぽっ！</div>
        <div class="desc">即売会サークルのためのレジ・会計アプリ｜秒会計・おつり自動計算・取り置き予約管理・売上/確定申告の集計</div>
        <div class="meta">近日公開・iPhone / Android</div>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow">&rsaquo;</div>
    </a>

    <!--
    <a class="card" href="/kyasuho/">
      <img class="icon" src="/kyasuho-support/icon.png" alt="きゃすりん" onerror="this.style.visibility='hidden'">
      <div class="body">
        <div class="name">きゃすりん</div>
        <div class="desc">コンカフェ特化の予約・店舗管理SaaS｜予約台帳・レジ・シフト・給与・経費・分析をひとつに</div>
        <div class="meta">開発中・Web / iPhone / Android</div>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow">&rsaquo;</div>
    </a>
    -->

  </div>

  <div class="section-label">BLOG</div>
  <div class="apps">
    <a class="card" href="/blog/">
      <div class="blog-badge">BLOG</div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="name">イベント攻略ブログ</div>
        <div class="desc">コミケ・同人イベントの攻略情報・初参加ガイド・サークル参加Tips</div>
        <div class="meta">記事を読む</div>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow">&rsaquo;</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; 瑠璃フクロウ ｜ X：<a href="https://x.com/rurifukuro">@rurifukuro</a> ｜
    お問い合わせ：<a href="mailto:rurifukuro@gmail.com">rurifukuro@gmail.com</a>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
